abstract: The Federal Reserve Bank of New York said on Thursday that it had wound down the final remnant of its rescue of the American International Group, generating a multibillion-dollar profit in the process.

lead_paragraph: 8:31 p.m. | Updated The government is one step closer to shedding its burden from the financial crisis.
